Default funnels:
- waitlist → invited → activated
- signup → onboarding complete → first dry-run scan
- signup → first backtest → first dashboard return
- developer portal → API key created → sandbox request
- marketplace view → plugin install → plugin run
- pricing view → checkout started → subscription started

