============================================================
API RESPONSE FORMAT
============================================================

All endpoints must use standard response shape:

Success:

{
  "ok": true,
  "data": {},
  "error": null,
  "timestamp": "ISO_DATE"
}

Error:

{
  "ok": false,
  "data": null,
  "error": {
    "code": "ERROR_CODE",
    "message": "Human readable message"
  },
  "timestamp": "ISO_DATE"
}

Required error codes:

- GA_DISABLED
- GA_READINESS_BLOCKED
- FINAL_SAFETY_GATE_BLOCKED
- RELEASE_TRAIN_NOT_FOUND
- ROLLOUT_NOT_FOUND
- RELIABILITY_VALIDATION_FAILED
- LOAD_TEST_BLOCKED
- CHAOS_TEST_BLOCKED
- API_VERSION_NOT_FOUND
- DEPRECATION_NOTICE_NOT_FOUND
- MARKETPLACE_V2_DISABLED
- LISTING_NOT_FOUND
- LISTING_NOT_CERTIFIED
- PACKAGE_SCAN_FAILED
- PACKAGE_SBOM_REQUIRED
- MARKETPLACE_REVIEW_REQUIRED
- INSTALL_POLICY_BLOCKED
- PARTNER_PROGRAM_DISABLED
- PARTNER_PROFILE_NOT_FOUND
- CERTIFICATION_FAILED
- TRUST_BADGE_NOT_FOUND
- PRODUCT_ANALYTICS_DISABLED
- ANALYTICS_OPTED_OUT
- LEGALOPS_DISABLED
- COMMERCIAL_PACK_NOT_FOUND
- DATA_REGION_NOT_SUPPORTED
- TENANT_ACCESS_DENIED

