============================================================

Phase 15 is complete only when:

- GA readiness system exists.
- Final safety gate works.
- GA launch is blocked when critical safety checks fail.
- Release train service works.
- Rollout service works in dry-run mode.
- Reliability validation works.
- Load-test dry-run works.
- Chaos-test dry-run works and blocks destructive scenarios.
- API versioning system exists.
